result.name: Sushi Shin Japanese Restaurant

reviews.text: Super fresh and friendly chef... Omakase lunch is great value of money
Pricey but very good food and service..!!

The restaurant is located in Tin hau, within walking distance from the MTR station.  The entrance is very small, but inside the restaurant is quite spacious and nice. Sashimi is very fresh and tender, service is also attentive.  Dinner has omakase menu around 1350 and more, but you can choose to order dishes separately.  Food quality is excellent
One of my favourite sushi joints in Hong Kong. Good value and fresh sushi lunch sets.
Great value for lunch, amazing quality and can choose your favorite sushi
